  {
    "hotel_id": "2231450",
    "hotel_url": "https://www.agoda.com/sulis-beach-hotel-and-spa/hotel/bali-id.html",
    "name": "Sulis Beach Hotel and Spa",
    "detail": "I stayed here with my boyfriend in Jun 2017. The hotel was newly opened so everything was clean and in tip top condition. We were particularly impressed by the big swimming pool with good views and the fried rice served for breakfast. I suggest that you skip the western option entirely since that tasted average at best. The fried rice however, was the best I’ve tasted in my entire life. I tried many other restaurants in Bali but none were close enough. We also enjoyed the clean spacious room with cable tv and fast wifi. The only thing that was disappointing was the massage we tried. The price was significantly more expensive than the others on the streets and yet the massage was below our expectations as the masseurs did not apply enough pressure despite our requests. Basically, the massage was overpriced and did not feel good. Overall, we strongly recommend this hotel because of its spaciousness, cleanliness, big pool, delicious fried rice, cable tv and fast wifi. But please skip the massage. We’ll definitely stay here again if we ever return to Bali.",
